f\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n再問佢老豆出院架啦<br />\n去啦"},{"pid":"551b55e6bab7856378e649558bce989dafa171af","tid":27221,"uid":5386,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T08:10:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去啦傻閪<br />\n<br />\n女都唔識媾<br />\n<br />\n仲扮幫朋友問<br />\n<br />\n去到陪佢就夠<br />\n<br />\n野都唔洗講<br />\n<br />\n佢會記一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係我啊都話,我都係咁諗,但條女屋企人都係到我朋友照去既好似有少少奇怪喎,又未係男朋友</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪當江湖救急陪個女仔囉<br />\n<br />\n講真 個女仔咁唔開心嘅時候有人陪住佢<br />\n<br />\n佢個心都會定好多<br />\n<br />\n實會加個男仔分"},{"pid":"5b08a7c173005b144ad9ac951c6abda4e6fce7af","tid":27221,"uid":10426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T08:10:56.000Z","msg":"幫推 連登有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申 A0 聽教學"},{"pid":"b6a2c05f9c17ab8efef74ff0f094302f38b5d61f","tid":27221,"uid":26446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T08:10:58.000Z","msg":"有冇詳細教學啊 真係唔知點處理啊屌  我朋友真係唔知點算"},{"pid":"64a5d63841a3f8707619767204c073f7aa5b1d95","tid":27221,"uid":19979,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T08:11:25.000Z","msg":"咪去下囉<br />\n可能睇到第二條仔攬緊佢呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ef3d630e9d2a20a5a52fa62e664d22338e7d789","tid":27221,"uid":8833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T08:11:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>是咁的 我朋友收到條女電話話佢老豆突然有事入左醫院<br />\n條女而家有少少無助 我朋友想去陪佢 但而家佢既身分又唔係咁岩做呢件事<br />\n想問下咁多位巴打 呢種情況應該點做先可以解決到呢個危機?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n果陣情況一樣<br />\n朋友身分同條女去<br />\n<br />\n利申：最後一齊左，拍左4年到依家"},{"pid":"e3b358a934d4ad0bbc7d71892791cec21ea92bfc","t